                            <comment id="134088" author="olivergierke" created="Tue, 13 Dec 2016 09:30:22 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;That should be in place now. I&apos;ve added a couple more advanced fixes that sort of relate to the same problem. We&apos;re now skipping merging of &lt;tt&gt;null&lt;/tt&gt; values completely and also back out on a potential non-collection source value.&lt;/p&gt;

